$^{3+}$ cation lone pair and its consequences on phonon transport properties\nof Bi$_2$O$_2$S.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 May 2022 16:13:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Nov 2022 05:29:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-22"}
