ilitate the study of 2D magnetic topological states,\nincluding WHS, QAH insulator, and magnetic mirror Chern insulator states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 May 2022 12:39:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-08"}
